160
00:21:29,519 --> 00:21:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ključan element.

161
00:21:31,359 --> 00:21:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] Pogotovo bih rekao iskreno ono za nas muškarce koji često to outsourcamo ženama..

162
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:41,359
