224
00:31:53,119 --> 00:31:59,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kako kvalitetno živjeti u 2024.

225
00:31:59,359 --> 00:32:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] ili 2025.

226
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:04,000
