233
00:32:42,319 --> 00:32:45,279
[SPEAKER_01] Znači primarno si razmišljao o zdravlju kad si.

234
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam te pitao.

235
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:50,319
